+
+
+```bash
+$ kubectl gadget run ghcr.io/inspektor-gadget/gadget/advise_networkpolicy:%IG_TAG%
+```
+
+## Flags
+
+No flags.
+
+## Guide
+
+First, we need to create an nginx deployment which can respond to our test requests. 
+
+```bash
